  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The last that I saw of Dr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Korczak was that at some point, when-- during the liquidation of the Warsaw ghetto, that I will come back to a little bit later, Dr.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Korczak-- an ordinance came out that the orphanage has to be delivered to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And-- and then there was a last-minute attempt still to save Dr.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Korczak, because he knew that these children are-- have to be delivered to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, he made a choice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He made several choices.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One of his choice was how to do it most mercifully for the children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was no way to hide them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So what he did-- what he did was he told the children that they are going to-- on a-- on a-- on an outing, on a picnic.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He gave them flags, and singing the 'Hatikvah,' he marched right into the office of Treblinka with them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[CRYING]",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
